Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.12,0:01:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.67,0:01:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.59,0:02:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.47,0:02:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now that's a handy Jinchuuriki.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.87,0:02:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But... how'd you know I was the intruder?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.24,0:02:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no birds like that in this desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.06,0:02:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.48,0:04:24.61,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs36\blur4\fax0.18\fad(614,515)\pos(692,541)}The Jinchuuriki of the Sand
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.13,0:04:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.12,0:05:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now that's a handy Jinchuuriki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.25,0:05:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But... how'd you know I was the intruder?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.67,0:05:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no birds like that in this desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.51,0:05:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.47,0:05:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What was that noise earlier?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.76,0:05:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're supposed to report immediately if something happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.60,0:05:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What... happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.48,0:05:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Kazekage...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.57,0:05:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean something strange got into the village?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.87,0:05:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Yura was supposed to have tightened village security.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually... we have been unable to contact Captain Yura.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.79,0:06:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Come again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.50,0:06:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, man... That Deidara had to go and turn this into a circus.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.63,0:06:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yura, you head on back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.14,0:06:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Things will get complicated if the guys from the village find you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.27,0:06:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Lord Sasori.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.06,0:06:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a move on, Deidara.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.40,0:06:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like to be kept waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.24,0:06:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Gaara! I'm coming in!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.00,0:06:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Kankuro, the Kazekage is fighting up in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.06,0:06:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.47,0:06:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Gaara...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.78,0:07:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The covert action is a failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.66,0:07:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But now... I don't have to bother looking for you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.98,0:07:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He's got the advantage, as expected...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.28,0:07:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a real mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.70,0:07:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.79,0:08:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This one is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.25,0:08:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A transformation of one of Naruto's Shadow Clones, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.26,0:08:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm finished if it even grazes me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.34,0:08:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ninja Battle Skills, part three...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.76,0:08:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ninjutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.18,0:09:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The speed of his seal forming...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.77,0:09:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's way too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.69,0:09:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs24\fad(200,200)}(Katon: Goukakyuu no Jutsu - Fire Style: Fireball Technique)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.69,0:09:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Katon: Goukakyuu no Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.09,0:09:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Kakashi-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.43,0:09:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs24\fad(200,200)}(Doton: Shinjuu Zanshu no Jutsu - Earth Style: Headhunter Technique)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.43,0:09:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Doton: Shinjuu Zanshu no Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.48,0:09:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,A Shadow Clone, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.41,0:10:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Suiton: Suiryuudan no Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.41,0:10:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs24\fad(200,200)}(Suiton: Suiryuudan no Jutsu - Water Style: Water Dragon Missile)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.66,0:10:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.78,0:10:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Using Fire Style, Earth Style and Water Style consecutively.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.53,0:10:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ordinarily that's totally impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He isn't called the "Copy Ninja" for nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.58,0:10:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I understand how amazing he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.88,0:10:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.76,0:11:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is going to be a long-drawn-out affair.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.51,0:11:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's still plenty of time until dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.89,0:11:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.81,0:11:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Things might just be settled more quickly than you'd expect...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.75,0:11:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Gaara...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.59,0:11:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost time...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.02,0:12:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The real show's about to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.14,0:13:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.70,0:13:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He uses strange explosives...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.58,0:13:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And he's able to guide them, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.88,0:13:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I've pretty much got it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.56,0:13:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I always knew, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.21,0:14:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sharingan is really something else, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.07,0:14:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.36,0:14:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But even more than that, the speed of his seal formation...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.15,0:14:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so fast it's tough for us to even get near him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.79,0:14:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Katon: Goukakyuu no Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.63,0:14:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Suiton: Suiryuudan no Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.31,0:14:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,For the time being, we won't have a prayer of getting the bells unless we can do something about both his hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.85,0:14:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.85,0:14:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That Kakashi-sensei's incredibly strong for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.03,0:14:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He's smarter than Shikamaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.11,0:14:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He has a better sense of smell than Kiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.74,0:14:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,His Sharingan is better than Sasuke's.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.95,0:14:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,His Taijutsu is better than Bushy Brow's.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.25,0:15:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's got way more experience than us...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.92,0:15:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But even Kakashi-sensei must have a weakness!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.67,0:15:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If we think hard about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.01,0:15:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,A weakness, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.28,0:15:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He does... have a weakness!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.20,0:15:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.29,0:15:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I never thought they'd make me use my Sharingan this much...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.59,0:15:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But, oh well... I should be able to hang on until sunrise...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.80,0:15:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've still got... Shuriken... and Kunai Knives.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.85,0:15:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whoops! Mustn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.85,0:16:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This isn't like the old days.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.35,0:16:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're too good for me to be able to fight them while reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.02,0:16:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I want to know what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.27,0:16:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It seems the main character in "Make-Out Tactics" has some sort of incredible secret...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.78,0:16:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't wait to read what's next...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.16,0:16:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.36,0:16:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you really figure out Kakashi-sensei's weakness?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.54,0:16:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be able to figure it out if you look back on his actions up until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.50,0:16:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit stalling already...\NWhat's his weakness, Naruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.34,0:16:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.56,0:16:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.27,0:16:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought he'd have a weakness like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.19,0:16:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,See?! It's clear if you think back on his actions up until now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.42,0:16:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.15,0:16:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,In addition to occupying both his hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.28,0:16:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,we might be able to seal off his Sharingan if things go well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.70,0:17:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And then if we seize the opportunity...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.95,0:17:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto, sure enough, you're the number one most unpredictable ninja!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.54,0:17:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Still, I was so pleased with how much they've grown that I ended up getting kind of carried away...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.97,0:17:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I guess this time I'll wait and see what kind of move they'll make.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.72,0:17:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that that's settled, the first strike will decide this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.47,0:17:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll make the first move!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.60,0:17:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.19,0:17:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.08,0:17:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,They're fast, this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.30,0:17:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Katsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.01,0:17:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Gaara!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.23,0:18:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,They're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.83,0:18:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're underestimating me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.70,0:18:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To think you'd attack me head-on like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.50,0:18:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.17,0:18:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go, Kakashi-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.51,0:18:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,At the end of "Make-Out Tactics"...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.47,0:18:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.30,0:18:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,As it happens, the main character...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.14,0:18:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's giving away the ending! N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.48,0:18:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.55,0:18:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can read his lips with my Sharingan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.84,0:18:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I still understand what he's saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.42,0:19:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,A ninja is supposed to read below what's underneath.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.84,0:19:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Sensei?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.97,0:19:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You got me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.15,0:19:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's just like an eggshell protecting what's inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.58,0:19:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But it's incredible that he was able to block the explosion completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.22,0:20:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sabaku Rou!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.22,0:20:03.89,Notas,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs24\fad(200,200)}(Sabaku Rou: Sand Prison)
